The paper discusses the use of web page titles as a means of discovering missing web pages, which is a topic related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and digital libraries (cs.DL). The study also involves analyzing the textual content of web pages, which falls under the category of natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper touches on issues related to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and cyberinfrastructure (cs.CY) as it deals with the preservation and accessibility of web content.
